<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mafia | Home</title>
    {{!-- <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"> --}}
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap');

*{
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    cursor: url(../image/cursor.png), auto;
}
body{
    /* background:linear-gradient(#5672cf,#0098B8); */
    background:linear-gradient(#0c0e12,#131924);
    min-height: 100vh;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

body::-webkit-scrollbar{
    display: none;
}
.wrapper{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    min-height: 110vh;
}
.nav{
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-around;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100px;
    line-height: 100px;
    z-index: 100;
}
.nav-logo p{
    color: white;
    font-size: 25px;
    font-weight: 600;
}
.nav-menu ul{
    display: flex;
}
.nav-menu ul li{
    list-style-type: none;
}
.nav-menu ul li .link{
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #fff;
    padding-bottom: 10px;
    margin: 0 25px;
}
.link:hover, .active{
    border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
}
.nav-button .btn{
    width: 130px;
    height: 40px;
    font-weight: 500;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 30px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: .3s ease;
}
.btn:hover{
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
}
.parallax {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    height: 100vh;
}
#text {
    position: absolute;
    font-size: 5em;
    color: #fff;
    text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
}
.parallax img {
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    pointer-events: none;
}

.sec {
    position: relative;
    /* colour here */
    background: #131924;
    padding: 100px;
}
.sec h2{
    font-size: 3em;
    color: #fff;
}
.sec .content-text {
    padding-top: 30px;
    font-size: 1em;
    color: #ffffffc9;
    font-weight: 300;
}



.title_dec{
    margin-top: 5%;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #6070ff;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: .4s ease;
}


.contentfont{
    text-align:justify;
    word-break:keep-all;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
}

.image-content{
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  width: 50%;
}
/* card */
.wrapper-card{
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 20%;
    margin-bottom: 6%;
}
.container {
    margin-top: -250px;
    height: 400px;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
    justify-content: start;
}

.card {
    width: 150px;
    border-radius: .75rem;
    background-size: cover;
    cursor: pointer;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    margin: 0 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    transition: .6s cubic-bezier(.28,-0.03,0,.99);
    box-shadow: 0px 10px 30px -5px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
}

.card > .row {
    color: white;
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: nowrap;
}

.card > .row > .icon {
    background: #223;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    width: 50px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    margin: 15px;
}

.card > .row > .description {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: 80px;
    width: 520px;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition-delay: .3s;
    transition: all .3s ease;
}

.description p {
    color: #ffffff;
    /* text-shadow: #000000; */
    padding-top: 5px;
}

.description h4 {
    text-transform: uppercase;
}

input {
    display: none;
}

input:checked + label {
    width: 600px;
}

input:checked + label .description {
    opacity: 1 !important;
    transform: translateY(0) !important;
}

.card[for="c1"] {
    background-image: url('./image/c1.jpg');
}
.card[for="c2"] {
    background-image: url('./image/c2.jpeg');
}
.card[for="c3"] {
    background-image: url('./image/c3.jpg');
}
.card[for="c4"] {
    background-image: url('./image/c4.jpg');
}

.alert {
    padding: 15px;
    background-color: #f44336;
    color: white;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
    border-radius: 5px;
}

.alert.success {
    background-color: #4CAF50;
}
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="nav">
        <div class="nav-logo">
            <p>Mafia</p>
        </div>
        <div class="nav-menu" id="navMenu">
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#" class="link active" onmousedown="error.play();">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="./login" class="link" onmousedown="audio.play();">Services</a></li>
                <li><a href="./creators" class="link" onmousedown="audio.play();">Creators</a></li>
                <li><a href="./about" class="link" onmousedown="audio.play();">About</a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </header>
    {{#if successMessage}}
        <div class="alert success">{{successMessage}}</div>
    {{/if}}

    {{#if errorMessage}}
        <div class="alert">{{errorMessage}}</div>
    {{/if}}

    <section class="parallax">
        
        <!-- image -->
         <img src="image/hill1.png" id="hill1">
         <img src="image/hill4.png" id="hill4">
         <img src="image/hill2.png" id="hill2">
         <img src="image/plant.png" id="plant">
         <img src="image/hill3.png" id="hill3">
         <img src="image/hill5.png" id="hill5">

         <!-- headline text -->
         <h2 id="text">Los Santos</h2>
         

    </section>

    <section class="sec">
        <h2>Mafia - UnderWorld Web </h2>
        
        <div class="content-text">
            
            <div class="wrapper-card">
                <div class="container">
                    <input type="radio" name="slide" id="c1" checked>
                    <label for="c1" class="card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="icon">1</div>
                            <div class="description">
                                <h4>Underworld Weapons</h4>
                                <p>Mafia has so much to offer -
                                Buy/Sell weapons</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <input type="radio" name="slide" id="c2" >
                    <label for="c2" class="card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="icon">2</div>
                            <div class="description">
                                <h4>Luxury Cars</h4>
                                <p>Add exclusive cars to your collections</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <input type="radio" name="slide" id="c3" >
                    <label for="c3" class="card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="icon">3</div>
                            <div class="description">
                                <h4>Demanding Property</h4>
                                <p>Villa/Building/Office/Bunglow - One time deal </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                    <input type="radio" name="slide" id="c4" >
                    <label for="c4" class="card">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="icon">4</div>
                            <div class="description">
                                <h4>Hire Mafia(s)</h4>
                                <p>Wanna do contract ? Find mafias here</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </label>
                </div>
            </div>


            <div class="contentfont">
            <p class="title_dec">#１ UnderWorld Weapons</p> <br>
            Need to upgrade your arsenal? We got you covered. From pistols to rifles to heavy weaponry, we have the firepower to keep you ahead of the curve in Los Santos.Just like Michael, Franklin, and Trevor, you can trust us to provide the best tools 
            for the job. So come on down, and arm yourself for any mission. Whether you're robbing a bank, taking down a rival gang, or just want to protect yourself from the crazy world of Los Santos, 
            we've got.<br><br>
            </div>

            <img src="" class="image-content" alt="">

            <div class="contentfont">
            <p class="title_dec">#２ Luxury Cars</p> <br>
            In Los Santos, your ride is your statement.  Whether you're cruising the streets in a sleek sports car, tearing up the off-road in a rugged 4x4, or just trying to blend in with a classic muscle car, we've got the perfect vehicle for you.
            Just like Michael, Franklin, and Trevor, you can upgrade your ride, adding the speed, power, and style you need to make a statement on the streets of Los Santos. 
            So come on down, and find the car.<br><br>
            </div>

            <img src="" class="image-content" alt="">

